<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>HAYAN — A sustainable lifestyle brand</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..40,300;0,9..40,400;0,9..40,500;1,9..40,300;1,9..40,400&family=DM+Mono:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

:root {
  --bg: #f3f3f3;
  --black: #1a1a1a;
  --mid: #888;
  --border: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  --pistachio: #b4dcc8;
  --font: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
  --mono: 'DM Mono', monospace;
  --nav-w: 200px;
}

html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

body {
  background: var(--bg);
  color: var(--black);
  font-family: var(--font);
  font-size: 15px;
  line-height: 1.6;
  overflow-x: hidden;
}

/* ── HEADER ── */
header {
  position: fixed;
  top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
  z-index: 200;
  background: var(--bg);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  padding: 0 24px;
  height: 48px;
}
.hdr-left { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 20px; }
.hdr-brand { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.03em; }
.hdr-collab { font-size: 11px; font-family: var(--mono); opacity: 0.45; letter-spacing: 0.08em; }
.hdr-right { font-size: 11px; font-family: var(--mono); opacity: 0.45; letter-spacing: 0.08em; }

/* ── LAYOUT ── */
.layout { display: flex; padding-top: 48px; }

/* ── SIDEBAR NAV ── */
.sidebar {
  width: var(--nav-w);
  flex-shrink: 0;
  position: sticky;
  top: 48px;
  height: calc(100vh - 48px);
  padding: 32px 20px;
  border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 2px;
  overflow-y: auto;
}
.sidebar a {
  display: block;
  font-size: 12px;
  font-family: var(--mono);
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  color: var(--black);
  text-decoration: none;
  opacity: 0.35;
  padding: 5px 0;
  transition: opacity 0.15s;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}
.sidebar a:hover, .sidebar a.active { opacity: 1; }

/* ── MAIN ── */
main { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }

/* ── SECTIONS ── */
section {
  padding: 72px 48px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
}
section:first-child { padding-top: 80px; }

.sec-label {
  font-size: 11px;
  font-family: var(--mono);
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  opacity: 0.4;
  margin-bottom: 32px;
}

.sec-h2 {
  font-size: clamp(28px, 3.5vw, 48px);
  font-weight: 300;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  line-height: 1.15;
  margin-bottom: 28px;
  max-width: 700px;
}

.sec-body {
  font-size: 15px;
  line-height: 1.72;
  font-weight: 300;
  max-width: 620px;
  opacity: 0.75;
}
.sec-body p + p { margin-top: 16px; }

/* ── HERO ── */
#s-intro { padding-top: 80px; }
.hero-title {
  font-size: clamp(72px, 14vw, 180px);
  font-weight: 300;
  letter-spacing: -0.05em;
  line-height: 0.88;
  margin-bottom: 48px;
}
.explore-btn {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
  font-size: 12px;
  font-family: var(--mono);
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--black);
  text-decoration: none;
  border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
  padding: 10px 20px;
  margin-bottom: 60px;
  transition: background 0.15s, color 0.15s;
}
.explore-btn:hover { background: var(--black); color: var(--bg); }
.explore-btn::after { content: '↓'; }

.intro-body {
  font-size: 18px;
  line-height: 1.75;
  font-weight: 300;
  max-width: 680px;
  margin-bottom: 40px;
  opacity: 0.8;
}

/* ── IMAGE PLACEHOLDER ── */
.img-ph {
  background: #ddd;
  background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(-45deg, rgba(0,0,0,0.03), rgba(0,0,0,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px, transparent 8px);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 6px;
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 9px;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  position: relative;
}
.img-ph.dark {
  background: #1a1a1a;
  background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(-45deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.03), rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px, transparent 8px);
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
}
.img-ph.mint {
  background: var(--pistachio);
  background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(-45deg, rgba(0,0,0,0.04), rgba(0,0,0,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px, transparent 8px);
  color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
}

/* ── GRIDS ── */
.grid-2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2px; }
.grid-3 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 2px; }
.grid-4 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 2px; }
.grid-auto { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(180px, 1fr)); gap: 2px; }

/* ── STATEMENT / PULL QUOTE ── */
.statement {
  font-size: clamp(24px, 3.5vw, 42px);
  font-weight: 300;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  line-height: 1.3;
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: 48px 0;
  opacity: 0.85;
}

.pull-quote {
  font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 52px);
  font-weight: 300;
  letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  line-height: 1.2;
  max-width: 900px;
  margin: 56px 0;
  font-style: italic;
}

/* ── COLOR PALETTE ── */
.palette-section { margin: 40px 0; }
.palette-label {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  opacity: 0.45;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
}
.palette-label::before {
  content: '';
  display: inline-block;
  width: 12px;
  height: 12px;
  background: var(--pistachio);
  border-radius: 50%;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.palette-row {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(6, 1fr);
  gap: 0;
  margin-bottom: 4px;
  max-width: 600px;
}
.swatch {
  aspect-ratio: 1;
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-end;
  padding: 8px;
  position: relative;
}
.swatch-hex {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 9px;
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  line-height: 1.2;
}
.swatch.light-text .swatch-hex { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6); }

/* ── LOGO DISPLAY ── */
.logo-display {
  background: var(--bg);
  aspect-ratio: 16/9;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  font-size: clamp(48px, 8vw, 96px);
  font-weight: 300;
  letter-spacing: -0.04em;
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  margin: 24px 0;
}

/* ── SUBSECTION ── */
.subsec { margin-top: 56px; }
.subsec-label {
  font-size: 11px;
  font-family: var(--mono);
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  opacity: 0.35;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  padding-bottom: 12px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
}

/* ── STATS ── */
.stats-row {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 32px;
  margin: 40px 0;
  max-width: 700px;
}
.stat-num {
  font-size: clamp(40px, 5vw, 64px);
  font-weight: 300;
  letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  line-height: 1;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.stat-label {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  opacity: 0.5;
}

/* ── RETAILER LOGO GRID ── */
.retail-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  gap: 1px;
  background: var(--border);
  margin: 24px 0;
  max-width: 800px;
}
.retail-cell {
  background: var(--bg);
  aspect-ratio: 5/2;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 10px;
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  opacity: 0.6;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 8px;
}

/* ── CUSTOMER QUOTES ── */
.quote-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 24px;
  margin: 32px 0;
  max-width: 900px;
}
.quote-card {
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  padding: 24px;
}
.quote-text {
  font-size: 22px;
  font-weight: 300;
  line-height: 1.4;
  letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}
.quote-trans {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  opacity: 0.5;
}

/* ── SUMMARY TABLE ── */
.summary-table {
  width: 100%;
  border-collapse: collapse;
  font-size: 13px;
  max-width: 900px;
}
.summary-table th {
  text-align: left;
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 10px;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  opacity: 0.4;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  padding: 10px 16px;
  font-weight: 400;
}
.summary-table td {
  padding: 14px 16px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  vertical-align: top;
}
.summary-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
.tag-row { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6px; }
.tag {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  padding: 6px 12px;
  font-size: 12px;
  font-family: var(--mono);
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
}

/* ── FOOTER ── */
footer {
  padding: 48px;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
}
.footer-copy {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 11px;
  opacity: 0.35;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
}

/* ── SCROLL REVEAL ── */
.r {
  opacity: 0;
  transform: translateY(20px);
  transition: opacity 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1), transform 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
}
.r.in { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
.r.d1 { transition-delay: 0.08s; }
.r.d2 { transition-delay: 0.16s; }

/* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .sidebar { display: none; }
  section { padding: 48px 24px; }
  .grid-3, .grid-4 { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  .quote-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .stats-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .retail-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- HEADER -->
<header>
  <div class="hdr-left">
    <div class="hdr-brand">HAYAN</div>
    <div class="hdr-collab">Co-founder · Design Director</div>
  </div>
  <div class="hdr-right">2021</div>
</header>

<div class="layout">

  <!-- SIDEBAR -->
  <nav class="sidebar" id="sidebar">
    <a href="#s-intro" class="active">Intro</a>
    <a href="#s-brief">The brief</a>
    <a href="#s-problem">The problem</a>
    <a href="#s-insight">The insight</a>
    <a href="#s-logo">Logo</a>
    <a href="#s-identity">Identity</a>
    <a href="#s-material">Material</a>
    <a href="#s-product">Product</a>
    <a href="#s-cmf">CMF</a>
    <a href="#s-packaging">Packaging</a>
    <a href="#s-system">System</a>
    <a href="#s-outcome">Outcome</a>
    <a href="#s-summary">Summary</a>
  </nav>

  <main>

    <!-- ═══ 01 INTRO ═══ -->
    <section id="s-intro">
      <h1 class="hero-title r">HAYAN</h1>
      <a href="#s-brief" class="explore-btn r d1">Explore</a>
      <p class="intro-body r d1">
        A sustainable lifestyle brand. Its first product is a biodegradable toothbrush — not because the brand is about toothbrushes, but because the toothbrush is one of the most overlooked objects in the daily ritual of waste.
      </p>
      <p class="intro-body r d2">
        In Korea alone, 200 million toothbrushes are produced each year. None get recycled.
      </p>
      <div class="img-ph mint r" style="height:60vh;min-height:400px;margin-top:32px">
        <span>Hero — adult + kids toothbrush in pistachio mint, bathroom counter</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══ 02 THE BRIEF ═══ -->
    <section id="s-brief">
      <div class="sec-label r">The brief, and the reframe</div>
      <h2 class="sec-h2 r">The brief was a toothbrush.</h2>
      <p class="sec-body r">
        Econnect, a Korean PLA bioplastic manufacturer, asked me to design a biodegradable toothbrush that could compete with bamboo. I came back with a different answer: a better toothbrush wouldn't break out of the eco category. A different brand would.
      </p>
      <p class="sec-body r" style="margin-top:16px">
        I came on as co-founder, leading creative direction end-to-end.
      </p>
      <div class="pull-quote r">
        "They came for a toothbrush. I gave them a brand."
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══ 03 THE PROBLEM ═══ -->
    <section id="s-problem">
      <div class="sec-label r">The problem</div>
      <h2 class="sec-h2 r">The category was apologetic.</h2>
      <p class="sec-body r">
        Eco-friendly toothbrushes were almost all bamboo, prone to mold in humid bathrooms. They looked like a guilt purchase — earthy, muted, designed for the people who already cared.
      </p>
      <div class="grid-3 r" style="margin-top:32px">
        <div class="img-ph" style="aspect-ratio:1"><span>Competitor 01 — bamboo</span></div>
        <div class="img-ph" style="aspect-ratio:1"><span>Competitor 02 — bamboo</span></div>
        <div class="img-ph" style="aspect-ratio:1"><span>Competitor 03 — bamboo</span></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══ 04 THE INSIGHT ═══ -->
    <section id="s-insight">
      <div class="sec-label r">The insight</div>
      <div class="pull-quote r">
        What if a sustainable toothbrush didn't announce its sustainability?
      </div>
      <p class="sec-body r">
        Reach the consumer who isn't already eco-conscious — but who would prefer a sustainable option if it didn't cost them anything in feel or form.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══ 05 LOGO ═══ -->
    <section id="s-logo">
      <div class="sec-label r">Logo</div>
      <h2 class="sec-h2 r">A wordmark that whispers.</h2>
      <p class="sec-body r">
        Soft, lowercase, considered. The mark sits comfortably on a bathroom counter without competing for attention — designed to belong to the object, not announce it.
      </p>
      <div class="logo-display r">hayan</div>
      <div class="grid-2 r">
        <div class="img-ph" style="aspect-ratio:4/3"><span>Logo on packaging</span></div>
        <div class="img-ph" style="aspect-ratio:4/3"><span>Logo at small scale</span></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══ 06 IDENTITY ═══ -->
    <section id="s-identity">
      <div class="sec-label r">Brand identity</div>
      <h2 class="sec-h2 r">The system.</h2>
      <p class="sec-body r">
        Typography, color, and voice — built to feel like home, not like an eco brand.
      </p>
      <div class="img-ph r" style="height:60vh;min-height:400px;margin-top:32px">
        <span>Brand specimen — type lockup, color palette, applications</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══ 07 MATERIAL ═══ -->
    <section id="s-material">
      <div class="sec-label r">The material</div>
      <h2 class="sec-h2 r">PLA, not bamboo.</h2>
      <p class="sec-body r">
        Corn-based bioplastic. Decomposes in 6–12 months versus 500+ years. 70% less carbon in manufacturing. Higher elasticity than conventional plastic — better for toothbrushes.
      </p>
      <p class="sec-body r" style="margin-top:16px">
        It also doesn't absorb moisture. Bamboo's mold problem, gone.
      </p>
      <div class="grid-2 r" style="margin-top:32px">
        <div class="img-ph" style="aspect-ratio:4/3"><span>PLA pellets</span></div>
        <div class="img-ph" style="aspect-ratio:4/3"><span>Material detail — handle close-up</span></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══ 08 PRODUCT DESIGN ═══ -->
    <section id="s-product">
      <div class="sec-label r">Product design</div>
      <h2 class="sec-h2 r">Form driven by experience.</h2>
      <p class="sec-body r">
        Handle angled toward the bristle head — easier reach to back molars. Bristle count increased from 1,000 to 2,500 for a denser, softer brush. Children's version rounded to encourage lighter pressure — designed with how kids actually grip, not against it.
      </p>
      <div class="img-ph dark r" style="height:60vh;min-height:400px;margin-top:32px">
        <span>Hero product render — adult toothbrush, side profile</span>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-4 r" style="margin-top:2px">
        <div class="img-ph" style="aspect-ratio:1"><span>Handle profile</span></div>
        <div class="img-ph" style="aspect-ratio:1"><span>Bristle close-up</span></div>
        <div class="img-ph" style="aspect-ratio:1"><span>Adult vs kids</span></div>
        <div class="img-ph" style="aspect-ratio:1"><span>Kids' rounded form</span></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══ 09 CMF ═══ -->
    <section id="s-cmf">
      <div class="sec-label r">CMF</div>
      <h2 class="sec-h2 r">Pistachio mint, not earth tones.</h2>
      <p class="sec-body r">
        Eco products at the time leaned earthy and apologetic. HAYAN launched in pistachio mint — a soft, gen-Z-coded shade that doesn't read as "eco." It reads as home. An object you leave out on the counter, not one you hide in a drawer.
      </p>
      <p class="sec-body r" style="margin-top:16px">
        Adult and kids' toothbrushes shipped in the same pistachio at launch — a household system, not a single SKU.
      </p>

      <div class="palette-section r">
        <div class="palette-label">Launch palette</div>
        <div class="palette-row">
          <div class="swatch" style="background:#b4dcc8"><span class="swatch-hex">#B4DCC8</span></div>
          <div class="swatch" style="background:#e8e8e0"><span class="swatch-hex">#E8E8E0</span></div>
          <div class="swatch" style="background:#f3f3f3"><span class="swatch-hex">#F3F3F3</span></div>
          <div class="swatch light-text" style="background:#1a1a1a"><span class="swatch-hex">#1A1A1A</span></div>
          <div class="swatch" style="background:#d4d4cc"><span class="swatch-hex">#D4D4CC</span></div>
          <div class="swatch" style="background:#c8d8d0"><span class="swatch-hex">#C8D8D0</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="img-ph mint r" style="height:60vh;min-height:400px;margin-top:32px">
        <span>Mood shot — pistachio dominant, styled bathroom counter</span>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-2 r" style="margin-top:2px">
        <div class="img-ph mint" style="aspect-ratio:4/3"><span>Adult + kids together</span></div>
        <div class="img-ph mint" style="aspect-ratio:4/3"><span>Lifestyle detail</span></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══ 10 PACKAGING ═══ -->
    <section id="s-packaging">
      <div class="sec-label r">Packaging</div>
      <h2 class="sec-h2 r">Bold message, refined material.</h2>
      <p class="sec-body r">
        Eco packaging whispered. HAYAN announced itself — <em>I'm not plastic.</em> — in oversized type on uncoated kraft. Confidence without loudness.
      </p>
      <div class="img-ph r" style="height:60vh;min-height:400px;margin-top:32px">
        <span>Hero packaging shot — "I'm not plastic."</span>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-3 r" style="margin-top:2px">
        <div class="img-ph" style="aspect-ratio:4/3"><span>Kraft material detail</span></div>
        <div class="img-ph" style="aspect-ratio:4/3"><span>Typography close-up</span></div>
        <div class="img-ph" style="aspect-ratio:4/3"><span>Shelf comparison</span></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══ 11 SYSTEM ═══ -->
    <section id="s-system">
      <div class="sec-label r">The system</div>
      <h2 class="sec-h2 r">A product designed to come back.</h2>
      <p class="sec-body r">
        QR code on the packaging links to a return service. Used toothbrushes get mailed back. Subscription handles replenishment. The brand owns the full lifecycle.
      </p>
      <div class="img-ph r" style="height:55vh;min-height:380px;margin-top:32px">
        <span>Lifecycle diagram — Buy → Use → Return → Recycle</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══ 12 OUTCOME ═══ -->
    <section id="s-outcome">
      <div class="sec-label r">Outcome</div>
      <h2 class="sec-h2 r">The brand earned its sales without buying them.</h2>

      <div class="stats-row r">
        <div>
          <div class="stat-num">1,495%</div>
          <div class="stat-label">of crowdfunding goal</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="stat-num">285</div>
          <div class="stat-label">launch backers</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="stat-num">15+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">retail partners</div>
        </div>
